Learning Resources

Documentation

     * [https://facebook.github.io/relay/docs/getting-started.html#content
       ]Official Docs - Official Relay documentation.

FAQs

     * [https://gist.github.com/wincent/598fa75e22bdfa44cf47]Unofficial
       Relay FAQ - Common questions answered! Relay resources are scarce
       at the moment, so this is very helpful if you get stuck.

Tutorials

     * [https://auth0.com/blog/2015/10/06/getting-started-with-relay/]Gett
       ing Started with Relay - One of the few detailed walk throughs of
       hand-on Relay.
     * [https://medium.com/@clayallsopp/relay-101-building-a-hacker-news-c
       lient-bb8b2bdc76e6#.1i64q1pf9]Relay 101: Building A Hacker News
       Client - A complete workable example.
          + [https://medium.com/@clayallsopp/relay-102-mutations-d8b471a47
            30e#.i9vuv3vxl]Relay 102: Mutations - A follow up to "Relay
            101" concentrating on mutations.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sP3n-nht0Xo]Facebook Relay talk -
       Lunch and Learn session - Walkthrough of building a simple app, and
       demonstration of [https://github.com/graphql/graphiql]GraphiQL.
     * [http://blog.pathgather.com/blog/a-beginners-guide-to-relay-mutatio
       ns]A Beginner's Guide to Relay Mutations - Mutations in depth.
     * [https://learnrelay.org/]Learn Relay - Shows you how to make a
       Pokemon-themed CRUD app, providing a personal, cloud-based GraphQL
       backend so you can focus on the client-side code.

Overviews

     * [http://www.sitepoint.com/react-data-fetching-with-relay/]React
       Data Fetching with Relay - Clear conceptual overview of Relay's
       moving parts and magic.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IrgHurBjQbg]Joseph Savona - Relay:
       An Application Framework For React - Conceptual overview of Relay
       from the Facebook team.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X6YbAKiLCLU]F8 2015 - React Native
       & Relay: Bringing Modern Web Techniques to Mobile - Overview of
       Relay, some about the philosophy.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvWTxy1eY6s]Relay - Daniel Dembach
       - Hamburg React.js Meetup - A good general overview of Relay, some
       discussion of alternatives. Common questions are covered in Q&A at
       the end.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sP3n-nht0Xo]Facebook Relay talk -
       Lunch and Learn session - Walkthrough of building a simple app, and
       demonstration of [https://github.com/graphql/graphiql]GraphiQL.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cfna8gwt9h8]React with Relay and
       GraphQL with Andrew Smith - High level overview of Relay and
       GraphQL, with some useful discussion from the audience. Some
       discussion of other front-end frameworks, as well.
     * [http://sgwilym.github.io/relay-visual-learners/]Relay for Visual
       Learners - Very clear set of diagrams laying out how the different
       parts of Relay relate to each other.
     * [http://www.slideshare.net/BrooklynZelenka/relay-seamless-syncing-f
       or-react-vanjs]Relay: Seamless Syncing For React - An overview of
       what Relay is, and some discussion of experience using it in
       production.
     * Cartoon Intro to Facebook's Relay - An overview of how Relay works,
       complete with illustrations.
          + [https://code-cartoons.com/a-cartoon-intro-to-facebook-s-relay
            -part-1-3ec1a127bca5]Part 1: Saying what data you need with
            GraphQL
          + [https://code-cartoons.com/a-cartoon-intro-to-facebook-s-relay
            -part-2-d4a2435aee59]Part 2: Fetching data from the server
          + [https://code-cartoons.com/a-cartoon-intro-to-facebook-s-relay
            -part-3-9d8fcf8db670]Part 3: Syncing changes back up to the
            server
          + [https://code-cartoons.com/a-cartoon-intro-to-facebook-s-relay
            -part-4-aef7d819a8ed]Part 4: How it all fits together

Example Implementations

     * [https://github.com/taion/relay-todomvc]Relay TODO MVC - The
       classic TODO example app, written with Relay.
     * [https://github.com/transedward/relay-chat]relay-chat - Relay with
       routing and pagination.
     * [https://github.com/chentsulin/koa-graphql-relay-example]koa-graphq
       l-relay-example - "TODO" app with
       [https://github.com/chentsulin/koa-graphql]koa-graphql and relay.
     * [https://github.com/sogko/todomvc-relay-go]todomvc-relay-go - Relay
       TodoMVC app, driven by a Golang GraphQL backend.

Lists of Lists

     * [https://quip.com/oLxzA1gTsJsE]Relay and GraphQL Introduction
       Materials

Ecosystem

Libraries & Packages

     * [https://github.com/graphql/graphql-relay-js]graphql-relay-js -
       Simplifies creating a JS GraphQL server for react-relay.
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/babel-relay-plugin]Babel Relay
       Plugin - Use Relay the latest ES6+ syntax.
     * [https://github.com/relay-tools/react-router-relay]react-router-rel
       ay - react-router bindings for Relay. Greatly simplifies many local
       state UI uses cases.
          + [https://medium.com/@cpojer/relay-and-routing-36b5439bad9#.h91
            614i65]Relay and Routing - A well-articulated walk through of
            react-router-relay, and the problems that it solves.
          + [https://www.npmjs.com/package/relay-nested-routes]relay-neste
            d-routes - Generate nested routes that reflect nested data.
            Helpful for managing deep data.
          + [https://github.com/denvned/isomorphic-relay-router]isomorphic
            -relay-router - Server side rendering support for
            react-router-relay.
     * [https://github.com/4Catalyzer/relay-decorators]relay-decorator -
       Simply syntax for Relay containers with ES7 decorators (@ syntax)
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/recompose-relay]recompose-relay -
       Ease composition of Relay containers by currying and providing the
       component after the container.
     * [https://github.com/relay-tools/relay-local-schema]relay-local-sche
       ma - Use a local schema; no need for a remote GraphQL server.
     * [https://github.com/lenaten/react-native-relay]react-native-relay -
       Use Relay with React Native.
          + May be supported
            [https://github.com/facebook/relay/issues/26]out of the box in
            the future.
     * [https://github.com/acdlite/relay-sink]relay-sink - Use Relay to
       fetch and store data outside of a React component.
     * [https://github.com/guymers/babel-plugin-flow-relay-query]babel-plu
       gin-flow-relay-query - Convert [http://flowtype.org/]Flow types
       into Relay fragments.
     * [https://github.com/MattMcFarland/sequelize-relay]sequelize-relay -
       Make Relay compatible with
       [https://github.com/sequelize/sequelize]sequelize.
     * [https://github.com/mikberg/relay-mongodb-connection]relay-mongodb-
       connection - Create Relay connections from MongoDB cursors.
     * [https://github.com/eyston/relay-composite-network-layer]relay-comp
       osite-network-layer - Compose your Relay Network Layer of many
       different Network Layers each with their own schema.
     * [https://github.com/nodkz/react-relay-network-layer]react-relay-net
       work-layer - A Network Layer that adds support for query-batching
       and middlewares. It additionally provides some useful middlewares
       such as for auth, for logging, etc.

Tooling

     * [https://github.com/graphql/graphiql]GraphiQL - A library to
       introspect GraphQL, test queries and mutations.
          + [https://github.com/skevy/graphiql-app]GraphiQL App - A
            standalone app for viewing GraphQL, introspection docs, and
            testing queries/mutations. Invaluable for debugging your Relay
            app.
     * [https://github.com/relay-tools/relay-local-schema]relay-local-sche
       ma - Use a local schema; no need for a remote GraphQL server.
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/babel-relay-plugin]Babel Relay
       Plugin - Use Relay the latest ES6+ syntax.

Starter Kits

     * [https://github.com/fortruce/relay-skeleton]Relay Skeleton - Relay
       project skeleton.
     * [https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit]Relay Starter Kit -
       An app that it already set up with a basic setup. Just clone and
       tweak to suit your needs!
     * [https://github.com/kriasoft/nodejs-api-starter]Node.js API Starter
       Kit - Boilerplate and tooling for building data APIs with Node.js,
       GraphQL and Relay
     * [https://github.com/mhart/simple-relay-starter]Simple Relay Starter
       - A Browserify version of the
       [https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit]Relay Starter Kit.
     * [https://github.com/codefoundries/UniversalRelayBoilerplate]Univers
       alRelayBoilerplate Boilerplate + examples for React Native (iOS,
       Android), React (isomorphic, Material-UI), Relay, GraphQL, JWT,
       Node.js, Apache Cassandra.
     * [https://github.com/nethsix/relay-on-rails]Relay on Rails Starter
       Kit - A barebones starter kit for Relay application on Rails
       server. Just clone and tweak!
     * [https://github.com/lvarayut/relay-fullstack]Relay Fullstack -
       Relay Starter Kit integrated with Relay, Express, Webpack, Babel,
       Material Design Lite, and PostCSS.

Relay-Specific Server Support

Go

     * [https://github.com/graphql-go/relay]Go Relay - A Go/Golang library
       to help construct a graphql-go server supporting react-relay.
     * [https://github.com/sogko/todomvc-relay-go]todomvc-relay-go -
       React/Relay TodoMVC app, driven by a Golang GraphQL backend.

JavaScript

     * [https://github.com/graphql/graphql-relay-js]graphql-relay-js -
       Simplifies creating a JS GraphQL server for react-relay.

Python

     * [https://github.com/graphql-python/graphql-relay-py]graphql-relay-p
       y - A library to help construct a graphql-py server supporting
       react-relay.

Ruby

     * [https://github.com/rmosolgo/graphql-relay-ruby]graphql-relay-ruby
       - Relay helpers for GraphQL & Ruby.

Rails

     * [https://medium.com/@gauravtiwari/graphql-and-relay-on-rails-first-
       relay-powered-react-component-cb3f9ee95eca#.c88zcoftn]GraphQL and
       Relay on Rails--First relay powered react component - Full walk
       through of a simple Relay setup, including clonable code.
     * [https://medium.com/@khor/relay-facebook-on-rails-8b4af2057152#.5hj
       ih9wms]Relay/GraphQL On Rails - A brief example of Relay with
       Rails, complete with several diagrams to aid in comprehension.
     * [https://github.com/nethsix/relay-on-rails]Relay on Rails Starter
       Kit - A barebones starter kit for Relay application on Rails
       server. Just clone and tweak!

Scala

     * [https://github.com/sangria-graphql/sangria-relay]sangria-relay -
       Relay support for [http://sangria-graphql.org/]Sangria.

Testing

     * [https://medium.com/@mikaelberg/writing-simple-unit-tests-with-rela
       y-707f19e90129]Writing Simple Unit Tests with Relay - An early
       first look at testing Relay.

